data.description: Explore contemporary living in Southaven, MS, with this 3-bed, 2-bath home built in 2020. Nestled in a new subdivision, the property features a modern design, chef's kitchen, and a luxurious master suite. Enjoy abundant natural light, a landscaped yard, and a covered patio for outdoor living. The two-car garage adds convenience, and the community offers proximity to amenities. Move-in ready and energy-efficient, this home provides a perfect blend of style and functionality. Don't miss the chance to make it yours! Schedule a showing today.
